--------- Kannada (from the KannadaTeX package)
---------(KannadaTeX is GPLed, but the authors have given permission
          to allow the use and bundling of their fonts with ITRANS.)

kan*.mf
kan*.tfm

NOTE: This archive contains only a few of the fonts from the KannadaTeX
package. Download the original KannadaTeX archive to obtain all the
*.mf font files - it contains .mf files for many different font sizes and
shapes.
Note that kanmain.mf is changed slightly from the original (mode= line
commented, and last line %end uncommented).

